bug.short_desc: Fedora 25 meiga: DNF error: NON-fatal POSTIN scriptlet failure in rpm package meiga
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1245242 Screenshot of kickstart error screen
Description of problem:
Including the package group @graphical-internet --optional
in kickstart for Fedora 25 breaks the kickstart installation with error:
DNF error: NON-fatal POSTIN scriptlet failure in rpm package meiga
Excluding package with
-meiga
helps to unbreak kickstart installation.
See screenshot attached.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): Fedora 25 x86_64
How reproducible: Always
Thanks for the report, looking into the issue.
meiga-0.4.3-5.fc25 has been submitted as an update to Fedora 25. https://bodhi.fedoraproject.org/updates/FEDORA-2017-875e12df0b

meiga-0.4.3-5.fc25 has been pushed to the Fedora 25 testing repository. If problems still persist, please make note of it in this bug report.
